      • getSource

        IItemSource getSource()
        Get the source of the items. This will be invoked exactly once per structure element build.

        If the call chain ever got into the old API, this will be called at least once per IStructureDefinition.survivalBuild(Object, ItemStack, String, World, ExtendedFacing, int, int, int, int, int, int, int, ISurvivalBuildEnvironment, boolean) call.

      • getActor

        EntityPlayer getActor()
